    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/1501b3a85a2d88505d536f56704473c1.poster.avif?t=1550845125\" width=590 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/1501b3a85a2d88505d536f56704473c1.webm?t=1550845125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/1501b3a85a2d88505d536f56704473c1.mp4?t=1550845125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《327公寓》是一款采用第一人称视角的恐怖冒险游戏，主要任务是逃出困住你的循环时空。故事发生在1923年至2016年间的埃利松多老宅，我们需要在不同的时代探索这座老宅。游戏过程中充满了难题，要想把它们一一解开，你必须进行时间之旅，在不同的时间点去同一处地方。<br><br><strong>老宅</strong><br>伊利亚松多家族的老宅充满了神秘与危险。你需要弄清楚老宅里发生了什么事情，以及你被困在这里的原因。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/bcd9d8145fdf73c0a8459e171d4d2b17.poster.avif?t=1550845125\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/bcd9d8145fdf73c0a8459e171d4d2b17.webm?t=1550845125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/bcd9d8145fdf73c0a8459e171d4d2b17.mp4?t=1550845125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>时间之旅</strong><br>对《327公寓》而言，传统的逻辑显得过时了。传统的解谜机制是“需要做什么”和“需要在哪里做”，我们在此基础上增加了“应该什么时候做”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/b8247a51460287ea456bd8f3b391779a.poster.avif?t=1550845125\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/b8247a51460287ea456bd8f3b391779a.webm?t=1550845125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/b8247a51460287ea456bd8f3b391779a.mp4?t=1550845125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>15个不同时间点</strong><br>随着游戏的深入，时空跳跃及情节碎片化的叙事特征会越来越明显，你也可以去更多的时间点旅行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/57e6e252481fb0d0fcf4f374cd609bed.poster.avif?t=1550845125\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/57e6e252481fb0d0fcf4f374cd609bed.webm?t=1550845125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>叙述碎片化</strong><br>起初一切都没有意义，但当你把拼图碎片拼在一起以后，你就会明白游戏中的每个人物都经历了哪些事情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/f95b306c6fc8d78040a083408a35b984.avif?t=1550845125\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><strong>陈年影片</strong><br>你在不同时期的老宅各处找到的第一人称视角影片扩展了叙述内容。也许只有这样你才能逃跑。你进入的新地点会推进故事发展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/3ecc5036b6b922edbda1a990cd21ad05.avif?t=1550845125\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><strong>强大的敌人</strong><br>在这些奇怪的生物面前，你只能逃跑。侦查每间房间，悄悄在房间之间穿行。意外碰到这些生物可能会要了你的命。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/936070/extras/52cae59895138fbca950edb318c25435.avif?t=1550845125\" width=600 height=240 /></span>",
